Fourth Department,

March, 1956*

(March 7, 1956) In the Matter of Harry Lambertson, Appellant, against Department of Correction et al., Respondents.

Not published with other decisions of March 7, 1956, ante, p. 929.— [Rep.

Motion to appeal on handwritten records denied on the ground that the papers fail to show merit to the appeal.
